main event: A witness observed a pulsating object in the sky while returning from Midnight Chow, believing it to be a UFO due to its erratic movements and characteristics.
interesting points: The object changed directions and back-tracked along a constellation,The sighting lasted approximately 10 minutes from 2315 to 2325,The observer initially thought it was a dim star or a missile launch,The object swelled in size and displayed brilliant colors before disappearing,The witness described its velocity as faster than any satellite they had seen.
sighted object: a stationary object resembling a flying saucer
witness description: an observer who was returning from Midnight Chow and glanced at the stars
